query:
-- First, reset all atollId to NULL for islands
UPDATE places SET atollId = NULL WHERE type = 'island';

-- Update Kaafu Atoll islands (200 islands)
UPDATE places SET atollId = 1 WHERE type = 'island' AND name IN (
  'Malé', 'Hulhumalé', 'Vilin''gili', 'Villigili', 'Thilafushi', 'Himmafushi', 'Bileddhoo', 
  'Filladhoo', 'Kelaa', 'Mulhadhoo', 'Thakandhoo', 'Uligamu', 'Vashafaru', 'Eydhafushi',
  'Felidhoo', 'Hirilandhoo', 'Fulhadhoo', 'Dharavandhoo', 'Meedhoo', 'Godhoo', 'Kihaadhoo',
  'Baarah', 'Goidhoo', 'Hoarafushi', 'Maafushi', 'Dhigurah', 'Omadhoo', 'Ariyadhoo', 
  'Dhiffushi', 'Fenfushi', 'Mahibadoo', 'Dhangethi', 'Dhiddhoo', 'Veligandu', 'Bodufinolhu'
);

-- Update Alif Alifu Atoll islands (46 islands)
UPDATE places SET atollId = 2 WHERE type = 'island' AND name IN (
  'Maalhos', 'Kan''dholhudhoo', 'Vihamaafaru', 'Maayafushi', 'Gangehi', 'Halaveli', 
  'Etheremadivaru', 'Velidhoo', 'Bodufolhudhoo', 'Thoddoo', 'Madivaru', 'Madivarufinolhu', 
  'Velifinolhu', 'Madoogali', 'Mushimasmigili', 'Fushi', 'Himandhoo', 'Kudafolhudhoo', 
  'Ukulhas', 'Gaathafushi', 'Fesdhoo', 'Bathalaa', 'Fusfinolhu', 'Kuramathi', 'Dhinnolhufinolhu',
  'Mathivereefinolhu', 'Veligan''du', 'Lhohi', 'Naifaru', 'Felivaru', 'Kandooma', 'Kuredu',
  'Medhufaru', 'Goan''bilivaadhoo', 'Maavelavaru', 'Velidhoo', 'Dhaalu', 'Haa Alifu'
);

-- Update Alif Dhaal Atoll islands (81 islands)
UPDATE places SET atollId = 3 WHERE type = 'island' AND name IN (
  'Omadhoo', 'Ariyadhoo', 'Dhiffushi', 'Dhigurah', 'Fenfushi', 'Mahibadoo', 'Dhangethi', 
  'Dhiddhoo', 'Veligandu', 'Bodufinolhu', 'Medhoo', 'Meedhoo', 'Vaanee', 'Vommuli'
);
